download BUDDY 2.4 (http://sourceforge.net/projects/buddy/)
apply the patch in ./patch on sources files (necessary if you use a Macintosh (performances problem))
compile and install BUDDY 2.4

make BUDDYLIB=<path2buddylib> BUDDYH=<path2buddh> 
     <path2buddylib> must contain file libbdd.a (/usr/local/lib/ by default)
     <path2buddh> must contain file bdd.h (/usr/local/include/ by default)

make install OR sudo make install